<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 20:06:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>惊慌失措的人们离开希法医院，据报道加沙北部学校有数十人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/panicked-people-leave-shifa-hospital-while-dozens-reportedly-killed-at-north-gaza-school/0000018b-e3d5-df9a-ab8b-ffdd46250000</link><description>撤离后只剩下以色列军队和骨干人员来照顾那些病重而无法移动的人。以色列表示，加沙北部的医院是其旨在镇压哈马斯的地面攻势的主要目标，声称这些医院被用作激进分子的指挥中心和武器库</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 19:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/panicked-people-leave-shifa-hospital-while-dozens-reportedly-killed-at-north-gaza-school/0000018b-e3d5-df9a-ab8b-ffdd46250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对派领导人拉皮德试图争取利库德集团成员的支持以推翻内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-trying-to-muster-support-from-likud-mks-to-topple-netanyahu/0000018b-e391-dffa-adef-e791daee0000</link><description>Yesh Atid 主席 Yair Lapid 希望在不信任投票中获得足够的支持，并与利库德集团等议员进行了交谈。然而，许多MKs可能会拒绝依赖阿拉伯政党，而他的反对党伙伴本尼·甘茨(Benny Gantz)在选举民意调查中有支持，他更愿意提前举行选举</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 19:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-trying-to-muster-support-from-likud-mks-to-topple-netanyahu/0000018b-e391-dffa-adef-e791daee0000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属游行抵达耶路撒冷，在内塔尼亚胡总理办公室前集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-march-reaches-jerusalem-rally-in-front-of-pm-netanyahus-office/0000018b-e326-d867-abab-f7a628140000</link><description>大约一万名游行者进入首都，随后将在特拉维夫举行另一场集会。这些家人稍后将会见以色列战时内阁的三名成员，而总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡尚未接受他们的邀请</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 16:31:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-march-reaches-jerusalem-rally-in-front-of-pm-netanyahus-office/0000018b-e326-d867-abab-f7a628140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全机构：哈马斯可能事先不了解新星节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-establishment-hamas-likely-didnt-have-prior-knowledge-of-nova-festival/0000018b-e2ee-d168-a3ef-f7fe8ca20000</link><description>以色列高级安全官员估计，哈马斯通过无人机或降落伞飞行者发现了诺瓦音乐节，并利用其通讯系统将恐怖分子引导至该地点</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 15:49:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-establishment-hamas-likely-didnt-have-prior-knowledge-of-nova-festival/0000018b-e2ee-d168-a3ef-f7fe8ca20000</guid></item><item><title>数百名布兰代斯校友威胁要停止捐款，除非亲巴勒斯坦组织恢复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/brandeis-alumni-threaten-to-stop-donations-unless-pro-palestinian-group-reinstated/0000018b-e2f0-df9a-ab8b-fef86a7a0000</link><description>在写给布兰代斯大学校长的一封信中，校友们表示，除非学校收回有效禁止巴勒斯坦正义学生组织在校园内举办活动的决定，否则他们将撤回资助。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 15:24:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/brandeis-alumni-threaten-to-stop-donations-unless-pro-palestinian-group-reinstated/0000018b-e2f0-df9a-ab8b-fef86a7a0000</guid></item><item><title>马斯克：“非殖民化”、“从河流到海洋”等术语将导致X暂停</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/musk-decolonization-and-from-the-river-to-the-sea-will-result-in-suspension-from-x/0000018b-e2ce-dffa-adef-e6ce41b40000</link><description>在一些全球最大的公司暂停了该平台上的广告后，马斯克写道：“明确呼吁极端暴力违反了我们的服务条款，并将导致我们的服务被暂停。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 15:16:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/musk-decolonization-and-from-the-river-to-the-sea-will-result-in-suspension-from-x/0000018b-e2ce-dffa-adef-e6ce41b40000</guid></item><item><title>坦桑尼亚宣布一名被哈马斯绑架到加沙的坦桑尼亚公民死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/tanzania-announces-death-of-one-of-its-citizens-kidnapped-by-hamas-in-gaza/0000018b-e24b-d168-a3ef-f7fb6b530000</link><description>22 岁的克莱门斯·费利克斯·马坦加 (Clemence Felix Matanga) 显然于 10 月 7 日在尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz) 被劫为人质。然而，目前尚不清楚他的死亡是如何得到确认的，也不清楚他的尸体是否已被找到</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 14:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/tanzania-announces-death-of-one-of-its-citizens-kidnapped-by-hamas-in-gaza/0000018b-e24b-d168-a3ef-f7fb6b530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军杀死五名约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人，称这是计划中的迫在眉睫的恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-kills-five-west-bank-palestinians-it-says-planned-terror-attack/0000018b-e17c-dffa-adef-e77c09630000</link><description>以色列军队袭击了纳布卢斯附近巴拉塔难民营内用作法塔赫运动总部的设施。巴勒斯坦人报告称，伤亡者中有一名 14 岁男孩</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 11:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-kills-five-west-bank-palestinians-it-says-planned-terror-attack/0000018b-e17c-dffa-adef-e77c09630000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布在加沙战斗中丧生的五名士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article-live/five-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-strike-rocket-sirens-sound-in-northern-israel/0000018b-e094-dffa-adef-e6942ae00000</link><description>以色列国防军：我们袭击了真主党目标，拦截了黎巴嫩境内的可疑空中目标 ■ 加沙医疗消息来源：以色列国防军袭击加沙南部汗尤尼斯的死亡人数上升至 64 人 ■ 以色列国防军：军队扩大了在加沙北部的行动，针对加沙城的其他社区■ 自10 月7 日以来，至少有1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙有 239 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：11,240 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 04:11:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article-live/five-palestinians-killed-in-west-bank-strike-rocket-sirens-sound-in-northern-israel/0000018b-e094-dffa-adef-e6942ae00000</guid></item><item><title>战争掩护下的人口迁移：探访定居者民兵被遗弃的土地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-11-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/population-transfer-under-cover-of-war-a-visit-to-the-forsaken-land-of-settler-militias/0000018b-df65-dffa-adef-ff6577300000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，16 个巴勒斯坦牧羊社区的居民被定居者赶出村庄。南希伯伦山现在由当地防卫队有效统治，这些防卫队在许多情况下由身穿制服的暴力定居者组成，他们正在进行人口转移</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 23:10:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-11-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/population-transfer-under-cover-of-war-a-visit-to-the-forsaken-land-of-settler-militias/0000018b-df65-dffa-adef-ff6577300000</guid></item><item><title>“美国犹太人现在将以色列视为一个处于危险之中、依赖他人的孩子”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/u-s-jews-now-see-israel-as-an-at-risk-dependent-child/0000018b-df36-d867-abab-dfb6c0e70000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，与过去一样，美国犹太人团结起来支持以色列的事业，并发起了大规模的筹款活动。但战争结束后他们对犹太国家的看法会怎样呢？哈佛大学犹太历史教授德里克·彭斯拉尔 (Derek Penslar) 访谈</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 22:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/u-s-jews-now-see-israel-as-an-at-risk-dependent-child/0000018b-df36-d867-abab-dfb6c0e70000</guid></item><item><title>“改变生活”的以色列初创公司在 10 月 7 日悲剧后收拾残局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/life-changing-israeli-startup-picks-up-the-pieces-after-october-7-tragedy/0000018b-decf-df9a-ab8b-decfedce0000</link><description>UBQ Materials 是一家位于内盖夫基布兹的初创公司，它完成了看似不可能的任务：将垃圾转化为有用的类似塑料的材料。 10 月 7 日，其两名员工被谋杀；其他人则失去了亲人或背井离乡。随后该公司跻身《时代》杂志“最佳发明”榜单</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 21:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/life-changing-israeli-startup-picks-up-the-pieces-after-october-7-tragedy/0000018b-decf-df9a-ab8b-decfedce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最好的防御是和解进攻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-best-defense-is-an-offense-of-conciliation/0000018b-de92-d867-abab-dfb6e60b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 20:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-best-defense-is-an-offense-of-conciliation/0000018b-de92-d867-abab-dfb6e60b0000</guid></item><item><title>如果内塔尼亚胡下台，对以色列来说是最好的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/it-would-be-best-for-israel-if-netanyahu-was-voted-out-of-office/0000018b-dd13-d168-a3ef-ddfb161c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 20:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/it-would-be-best-for-israel-if-netanyahu-was-voted-out-of-office/0000018b-dd13-d168-a3ef-ddfb161c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列右翼分子试图将加沙人口转移重新定义为“道德行为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-rightists-are-trying-to-reframe-a-gaza-population-transfer-as-a-moral-act/0000018b-d914-d423-affb-fbb7ddd30000</link><description>将阿拉伯人驱逐到其他国家的想法曾经与梅厄·卡哈内和其他极右激进分子联系在一起，因此被大多数以色列人视为厌恶。现在，令右翼分子高兴的是，这个想法正在作为战争的“道德”解决方案而受到关注</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 19:37:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-rightists-are-trying-to-reframe-a-gaza-population-transfer-as-a-moral-act/0000018b-d914-d423-affb-fbb7ddd30000</guid></item><item><title>“精神是这里最重要的武器”：与加沙的以色列军队并肩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/spirit-is-the-most-important-weapon-here-a-day-with-the-israeli-army-in-gaza/0000018b-dd67-df9a-ab8b-dfef50f70000</link><description>一名预备役军人在经过 41 天的战斗后说道：“四肢受伤、头部受伤、腹部受伤，我们什么都看到了。”</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 19:36:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/spirit-is-the-most-important-weapon-here-a-day-with-the-israeli-army-in-gaza/0000018b-dd67-df9a-ab8b-dfef50f70000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯是以色列无法改变的巴勒斯坦新精神的一部分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-part-of-the-new-palestinian-ethos-that-israel-cant-change/0000018b-ddcb-d423-affb-ffeba4ff0000</link><description>这场战争为该恐怖组织提供了任何未来的巴勒斯坦领导人都无法忽视的地位，包括目前被监禁的马尔万·巴尔古提 (Marwan Barghouti)</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 18:48:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-part-of-the-new-palestinian-ethos-that-israel-cant-change/0000018b-ddcb-d423-affb-ffeba4ff0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布86岁以色列人质视频引发人们对其生活的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/hamas-publishes-video-of-86-year-old-israeli-hostage-raising-concerns-about-his-life/0000018b-de30-dffa-adef-fe30c8880000</link><description>10 月 7 日，阿耶·扎尔马诺维奇 (Arye Zalmanovich) 在位于加沙边境附近基布兹尼尔奥兹 (Nir Oz) 的家中被绑架。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 16:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/hamas-publishes-video-of-86-year-old-israeli-hostage-raising-concerns-about-his-life/0000018b-de30-dffa-adef-fe30c8880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁批准向加沙地带供应加油车</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-approves-supplying-fuel-to-gaza-for-48-hours/0000018b-ddc8-df9a-ab8b-dfc854a70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理表示，在受到包括财政部长斯莫特里奇和国家安全部长本-格维尔在内的政府内部长的批评后，全体内阁将于周六召开会议</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 15:20:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-approves-supplying-fuel-to-gaza-for-48-hours/0000018b-ddc8-df9a-ab8b-dfc854a70000</guid></item><item><title>自以色列-加沙战争爆发以来，埃隆·马斯克和塔克·卡尔森领导了白人民族主义反犹太主义的爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/elon-musk-and-tucker-carlson-are-only-the-tip-of-the-antisemitic-iceberg-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-dd2d-d168-a3ef-ddff1ce20000</link><description>支持白人伟大更替理论的极右社交媒体人士也质疑对以色列的支持</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 13:54:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-17/ty-article/.premium/elon-musk-and-tucker-carlson-are-only-the-tip-of-the-antisemitic-iceberg-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-dd2d-d168-a3ef-ddff1ce20000</guid></item></channel></rss>